      "type": "file",
      "name": "Application.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Core/Application.h",
      "summary": "引擎核心 Application 类声明，采用单例模式管理应用生命周期，协调窗口（Window）、图层栈（LayerStack）和 ImGui 渲染层，是引擎运行的主入口。",
      "tags": ["entry-point", "core-system", "singleton", "application-lifecycle", "引擎核心"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用单例模式（s_Instance 静态成员）暴露全局 Get() 访问点；提供 CreateApplication 工厂函数由外部实现来创建派生类。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Core/Layer.cpp",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "Layer.cpp",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Core/Layer.cpp",
      "summary": "Layer 抽象基类的构造函数实现，接收调试名称并初始化 m_DebugName 成员。",
      "tags": ["core-system", "implementation", "层实现", "constructor"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Core/Layer.h",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "Layer.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Core/Layer.h",
      "summary": "定义 Layer 抽象基类，提供 OnAttach/OnDetach/OnUpdate/OnImGuiRender/OnEvent 等虚函数生命周期钩子，供派生类覆写以插入自定义逻辑。",
      "tags": ["core-system", "abstract-class", "layer-interface", "层抽象", "lifecycle-hooks"],
      "complexity": "simple",
      "languageNotes": "纯接口风格的抽象基类，所有虚函数提供空默认实现，派生类按需覆写，遵循好莱坞原则（Don't call us, we'll call you）。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Core/LayerStack.cpp",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "LayerStack.cpp",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Core/LayerStack.cpp",
      "summary": "LayerStack 类的实现，管理 Layer 指针的层叠结构：普通层（Layer）插入到指定位置并递增索引，覆盖层（Overlay）追加到末尾；析构时自动释放所有层内存。",
      "tags": ["core-system", "layer-management", "data-structure", "层栈管理", "memory-management"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:Engine/src/Himii/Core/LayerStack.h",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "LayerStack.h",
      "filePath": "Engine/src/Himii/Core/LayerStack.h",
      "summary": "LayerStack 类声明，基于 std::vector<Layer*> 实现层栈数据结构，支持 Layer/Overlay 的 Push/Pop 操作，提供双向迭代器接口以支持正向和反向遍历。",
      "tags": ["core-system", "layer-management", "data-structure", "层栈声明", "iterator-support"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 m_LayerInsertIndex 索引将容器分隔为 Layer 区和 Overlay 区，Layer 在前半部分、Overlay 在后半部分；提供 const 和非 const 两个版本的 begin/end/rbegin/rend。"
    },
    {
